According to the present invention, there is provided the following means:


<1> A thermoplastic resin foam, prepared by using a thermoplastic resin composition containing a melt-type crystallization nucleating agent (B) in a crystalline thermoplastic resin (A), which foam comprises a bubble having a mean bubble diameter of less than 1 μm in the inside thereof;

<2> The thermoplastic resin foam as described in the item <1>,

wherein a total reflectivity at a light wavelength of 550 nm is 100% or more in terms of an aluminum oxide ratio;


